 to, or employed in, any apprenticeship or other training program, in comparison with the total number or percentage of persons of such race, color, religion, sex, or national origin in any community, State, section, or other area, or in the available work force in any community, State, section, or other area.\u8217\'3f
\par 
}
}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li0 
