{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb200 
\u8216\'3fAn unlawful employment practice for an employer to give and to act upon the results of any professionally developed ability test provided that such test, its administration or action upon the results is not designed, intended or used to discriminate because of race, color, religion, sex, or national origin.\u8217\'3f
\par 
}
}
}
