}
}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb200 
 (3) Duke has, by plaintiffs\rquote  own admission, discontinued the use of discriminatory tactics in employment, promotions and transfers.
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
