{\field {\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://www.westlaw.com/Link/Document/FullText?findType=Y&serNum=1966119299&pubNum=345&originatingDoc=I8d60059c8f7b11d9a707f4371c9c34f0&refType=RP&fi=co_pp_sp_345_366&originationContext=document&vr=3.0&rs=cblt1.0&transitionType=DocumentItem&contextData=(sc.UserEnteredCitation)#co_pp_sp_345_366" }{\fldrslt 
