{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb200 
A. The Necessity for Job-Relatedness
\par 
}
}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li0 
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li0 
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
Whites fare overwhelmingly better than blacks on all the criteria,
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
{\*\bkmkstart co_fnRef_B01761970116358_ID0EUYBG_2}{\*\bkmkend co_fnRef_B01761970116358_ID0EUYBG_2}
