{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb200 
Title VII bars \u8216\'3ffreeze-outs\rquote  as well as pure discrimination, where the \u8216\'3ffreeze\u8217\'3f is achieved by requirements that are arbitrary and have no real business justification. Thus Duke Power\rquote s discrimination against all those who did not benefit from the pre-1955 rule for whites operates as an illegal \u8216\'3ffreeze-out\u8217\'3f of blacks from the inside departments.
\par 
}
}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li0 
