7
}}}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 but was defeated. We agree with the district court that a test does not have to be job-related in order to be valid under \u167\'3f 703(h).
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
