 and concentrating or \u8216\'3ftelescoping\u8217\'3f the effect of past years of discrimination against Negro employees into the present placement of Negroes in an inferior position for promotion and other purposes, that present result is prohibited, and a seniority system which operates to produce that present result must be replaced with another system.\rquote 
