{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs18 \li0 
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs18 \sa200 \sb0 
Standardized Tests. It is generally known that standardized aptitude tests are designed to predict future ability by testing a cumulation of acquired knowledge.
\par 
}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs18 \li0 
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs18 \sa200 \sb0 
In other words, an aptitude test is necessarily measuring a student\rquote s background, his environment. It is a test of his cumulative experiences in his home, his community and his school.
\par 
}
}
