The EEOC position has been elaborated in the new Guidelines on Employee Selection Procedures, 29 CFR s 1607, 
}
{\field {\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://www.westlaw.com/Link/Document/FullText?findType=Y&pubNum=0001037&cite=35FR12333&originatingDoc=I179302d09c1f11d993e6d35cc61aab4a&refType=FR&originationContext=document&vr=3.0&rs=cblt1.0&transitionType=DocumentItem&contextData=(sc.UserEnteredCitation)" }{\fldrslt 
