35 Fed.Reg. 12333 (Aug. 1, 1970)
}\b0 \cf21 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs18 \sa0 \sb0 }}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs18 \sa0 \sb0 
. These guidelines demand that employers using tests have available \u8216\'3fdata demonstrating that the test is predictive of or significantly correlated with important elements of work behavior which comprise or are relevant to the job or jobs for which candidates are being evaluated.\u8217\'3f
}
